{"tid":1983327,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【求吓大家】開個Twitter啦！唔洗寫字，report就得！","createTime":"2020-04-21T18:13:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T03:36:02.000Z","uid":300488,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c9d4ac60928bbfb2775d411e7203e4eabe65c2f2","tid":1983327,"uid":300488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T18:13:19.000Z","msg":"因為twitter主要用英文，所以好多人都唔用。<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跳出你嘅comfort zone</span></strong>?<br />\n<br />\n唔識英文咪齋 retweet 囉 （= fb share)<br />\n<br />\n其實五毛打手大部分都寫殘體，你係唔會睇唔明。(佢寫到1999除外）<br />\n<br />\n而家五毛不斷擴大緊個fake news圈，除咗啲「自由XX電台」，仲有好多假扮其他中外媒體acc，你report佢acc就得，唔洗同佢罵戰。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LeyrwPr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLeyrwPr.png&h=c7acaa7a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0S5ad2T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0S5ad2T.png&h=23c21a43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTwitter 好過爛書好多，基本上爛書都report唔到五毛，但Twitter 仲得！ 點解要放棄呢？<br />\n<br />\n你以為你英文差，但五毛仲差，錯曬grammar都不斷寫！ <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/356XDvq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F356XDvq.png&h=a8b9a09b&s={SIZE}\" /> （in the past 又點用 will?) <br />\n佢都係google translate (如果佢翻到牆嘅話）<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1eGs0Hf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1eGs0Hf.png&h=352090df&s={SIZE}\" /> 點解你唔可以查吓啲英文點解？<br />\n<br />\n都只不過係做一個冷氣軍師，你仲可以得閒先做。<br />\n而家即刻踏出第一步開acc先啦！<br />\n<br />\n利申：英文合格，唔洗讀毅進。"},{"pid":"24f428182d454e7e748681817ea26521812a30c8","tid":1983327,"uid":252069,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T19:08:01.000Z","msg":"強烈建議美國 &gt;立即&lt; 暫停香港關系法!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1983340\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1983340</a>"},{"pid":"0455e4eecca918ee0eb5002388de5bbd4ee356b5","tid":1983327,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike